# booping — /code-review

{% import "_partials/_available_agents.j2" as available_agents with context %}
Review changed code (diff, files, or directory) against layered, stack-aware checklists plus plan- and lesson-aware dynamic checks. Stateless side-skill — output is chat-only, no persistent report, no plan-lifecycle status.

This skill is **wide-domain** — it must work across very different stacks. Stack-specific rules live in checklist templates (core under `docs/review_templates/`, project-local under `~/Claude/{project}/review_templates/`). Project-specific concerns live there or in `_booping/skill_code-review.md`. Do not bake stack details into this skill.

